+### Run event streaming
 
-Server-Sent Events stream of the run's tool-call progress, token deltas, and lifecycle events. Designed for dashboards and thick clients that want to attach/detach without losing state.
+Run events (tool-call progress, token deltas, lifecycle) are persisted durably and observed via the resumable session subscription stream, `GET /api/sessions/{session_id}/subscribe` — the `POST /v1/runs` 202 response includes the `session_id` to subscribe to. Any number of clients can attach, detach, and resume from a cursor without losing events; see `docs/api-session-sync.md`. (The former single-consumer `GET /v1/runs/{run_id}/events` SSE stream was removed.)
 
